1. *Borbu* je izgubio čim se suočio sa protivnikom. (He lost the fight as soon as he faced his opponent.)
2. Njih dvoje su se *borbili* kroz čitavu noć. (They fought each other through the whole night.)
3. Naša družina je stvarno ozbiljno *borbila* da postane najbolja. (Our group was really fighting seriously to become the best.)
4. Ona je *borbala* sa svojim strahovima da bi prebrodila teške trenutke. (She was struggling with her fears in order to overcome the hard times.)
5. Ovaj rat će biti duga i teška *borba*. (This war will be a long and hard fight.)